  "title": "Tapping for Breath-Led Calm",
  "subtitle": "A tapping practice for reclaiming a steady breathing rhythm during the day and before sleep",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 9 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive. Two scripts: a daytime practice for shallow breath under stress, and a bedtime practice for breathing the day away into deeper sleep.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "categorySlug": "mindset",
