  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Two tapping scripts for Day 9 of the sleep arc. The first works with shallow stress-breathing during the day; the second is a bedtime practice for slowing the breath enough that the body follows into sleep."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "New to tapping? Read "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"}}],
            "text": "how EFT tapping works"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " first."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The practice"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Script 1: Reclaim a calm breathing rhythm"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though my breath has been shallow and tight, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though stress makes me forget to breathe, I honour how my body learned to cope."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though deep breathing feels unfamiliar, I'm open to letting it steady me today."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I notice how my breath stops short when I'm tense."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Quick, shallow breaths keep my system revved."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body reads that rhythm as a reason to stay alert."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can choose a new rhythm on purpose."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I inhale a little more space."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I exhale a little more pressure."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My breath is a message of safety to every cell."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body listens and begins to settle."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My breath is my anchor point."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I breathe in steadiness; I breathe out strain."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Each inhale expands calm through my chest and belly."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Each exhale releases effort from my shoulders and jaw."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My breathing sets the pace for peace today."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I trust this simple practice to quiet my system."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Calm spreads with every cycle."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I breathe freely and feel safe."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Script 2: Breathe the day away"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though my breath still sits high in my chest from the day, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though tightness tells my body to stay alert, I honour how it tried to protect me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though it feels restricted, I'm open to letting my breath widen and slow me into sleep."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I breathe the day out, slow and steady."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Inhale enough... exhale more."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Air moves deeper each time and my ribs begin to loosen."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My belly joins the breath and my back lets go."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I can hear my own breathing settle the room."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Each slow breath unwinds a layer of tension."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My whole body follows the rhythm toward stillness."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm carried by my breath into rest."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 4},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My breath is a lullaby to my nervous system."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " In with safety, out with strain."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm calm, heavy, and ready to sleep."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My breath keeps watch so I don't have to."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Every exhale deepens the quiet."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " My body trusts this rhythm completely."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Peace arrives on the next breath, and the next."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I breathe myself into deep, easy sleep."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times."}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adapted from Day 9 of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "italic"}],
            "text": "SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive to Fall Asleep Faster and Wake Energised"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (Rebecca J Page, 2025). The tapping framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), developed in the mid-1990s."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
